pp\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAUiEwjJ142quOuTAxW4g7oAHTN7M9tIqePMotqqzs08ygEEvG8sNw==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDc2Q3dmanFtd1pLeUcxMXJDYmFKTWhKR1RvQXxBQ3Jtc0trYkxQZE5mVkk0QjVWYnQ1dTM0clRfZTdmSzJZXzdkMURFamY0RzJjcjZ1SlVmd24tbmJLZXlITVU1cFhaeW1xNHg3RDNjbUNQTkpNbUp3ZzNHWmsxYmE0V1ZhVk9XWk1yam9mNmNoS1Ixcm96T3owVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=PJs5VaRTMak","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDc2Q3dmanFtd1pLeUcxMXJDYmFKTWhKR1RvQXxBQ3Jtc0trYkxQZE5mVkk0QjVWYnQ1dTM0clRfZTdmSzJZXzdkMURFamY0RzJjcjZ1SlVmd24tbmJLZXlITVU1cFhaeW1xNHg3RDNjbUNQTkpNbUp3ZzNHWmsxYmE0V1ZhVk9XWk1yam9mNmNoS1Ixcm96T3owVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=PJs5VaRTMak","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBMQ040EGAUiEwjJ142quOuTAxW4g7oAHTN7M9tIqePMotqqzs08ygEEvG8sNw==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbUdUR1VFM3lfVm1rSmNtVHRnaEZnMG1QMTlLUXxBQ3Jtc0ttRmVFX1V6ZzRvR19FY2tVbzhBTHJwa2dzSTNRM1NjTElFZ1AzbjN0Rm15UXhtb3lUdWQ3NlFpNmhqdU8zSkNxM2JQTVhyZkRMSmRieGl3cFcxejFs